title: Best of Toadies: Live from Paradise
description:
Best of Toadies: Live from Paradise is a live album by Toadies. It was recorded just prior to the band&#039;s breakup in 2001 and was released as a limited edition in March of 2002 on Aezra Records/Orpheus Music. It was re-released on July 13, 2004. The album proclaims: "No overdubs. Warts and all!"
